<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Uh, I don=E2=80=99t know, here=E2=80=99s one m=
odel for tech startups and venture capital:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Most of the returns to venture capita=
l come from making early-stage investments in companies that go on to chang=
e the world in radical and unexpected ways.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bott=
om: 5px;">Therefore, if you are a VC, you should make risky investments in =
visionary entrepreneurs with wild ideas: Many won=E2=80=99t work out, and <=
a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31919120.257399/aHR=
0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDItMjYvc3Rhcn=
R1cHMtc29tZXRpbWVzLXN0cmV0Y2gtdGhlLXRydXRoP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA2MjcyM19NT05FWVNUV=
UZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDYy=
NyZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB50bbc20c" itemp=
rop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color:=
 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;"> some will be frauds</a>,=C2=A0but one or two might hit it big, and the =
path to success is having one or two radical world-changing companies.=C2=
=A0</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Therefore, if you are a tech e=
ntrepreneur, you should try to come across as a wild-eyed visionary, becaus=
e VCs (correctly) look for that and will give you money.</li>=09<li style=
=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Therefore, if you are a tech entrepreneur, you sho=
uld take hallucinogenic drugs, in order to (1) be able to visualize an impr=
obable future and (2) be kind of weird to talk to.</li>=09<li style=3D"marg=
in-bottom: 5px;">If you are a tech venture capitalist, you should also take=
 hallucinogenic drugs, in order to get on the wavelength of the visionary e=
ntrepreneurs.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I do not mean to endorse this model too much o=
r anything, but here is a guy in the Wall Street Journal <a href=3D"https:/=
/link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31919120.257399/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3Nq=
LmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9zaWxpY29uLXZhbGxleS1taWNyb2Rvc2luZy1rZXRhbWluZS1sc2QtbWF=
naWMtbXVzaHJvb21zLWQzODFlMjE0P21vZD1ocF9sZWFkX3Bvczc/607f07ceef4b8524a319a2=
3cB1f7b11ad" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blan=
k" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom=
-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;">who believes it</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Spencer Shulem, CEO of the startup BuildBetter=
.ai, said he uses LSD about every three months because it increases focus a=
nd helps him think more creatively. While working alone after hours, he wil=
l sometimes take a low-enough dose where he said no one would know he was o=
n LSD. Other times, he=E2=80=99ll take a larger dose alone and connect with=
 nature on a hike.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Shulem, who lives in New York City, said the h=
igh expectations of venture-capital firms and investors in general can lead=
 founders to turn to psychedelics to provide an edge. =E2=80=9CThey don=E2=
=80=99t want a normal person, a normal company,=E2=80=9D he said. =E2=80=9C=
They want something extraordinary. You=E2=80=99re not born extraordinary.=
=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You=E2=80=99re not born extraordinary, but if =
you take enough drugs you will think you are extraordinary, and if they tak=
e enough drugs they=E2=80=99ll agree. The article is about how everyone in =
Silicon Valley is on drugs:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elon Musk takes ketamine. Sergey Brin sometime=
s enjoys magic mushrooms. Executives at venture-capital firm Founders Fund,=
 known for its investments in SpaceX and Facebook, have thrown parties that=
 include psychedelics.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Routine drug use has moved from an after-hours=
 activity squarely into corporate culture, leaving boards and business lead=
ers to wrestle with their responsibilities for a workforce that frequently =
uses. At the vanguard are tech executives and employees who see psychedelic=
s and similar substances, among them psilocybin, ketamine and LSD, as gatew=
ays to business breakthroughs.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThere are millions of people microdos=
ing psychedelics right now,=E2=80=9D said Karl Goldfield, a former sales an=
d marketing consultant in San Francisco who informally counsels friends and=
 colleagues across the tech world on calibrating the right small dose for m=
aximum mindfulness. It is =E2=80=9Cthe fastest path to opening your mind up=
 and clearly seeing for yourself what=E2=80=99s going on,=E2=80=9D said Gol=
dfield.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I do not generally look for pharmacological ex=
planations of social or business phenomena; I don=E2=80=99t, for instance, =
believe that FTX failed because <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/31919120.257399/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYnVzaW5lc3NpbnNpZGVyLmNvbS9zY=
W0tYmFua21hbi1mcmllZC1kcnVnLXVzZS1mdHgtYWxhbWVkYS1jYXJvbGluZS1lbGxpc29uLWFt=
cGhldGFtaW5lcy0yMDIyLTEx/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBab150f5b" itemprop=3D"Sto=
ryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; =
text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-c=
olor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">its emp=
loyees were all on Ritalin</a>.=C2=A0But it would be very funny if the stor=
y of the American tech industry in the 21st century, good and bad, is mostl=
y =E2=80=9CLSD and ketamine.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0The drugs help with business ide=
as:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Some entrepreneurs microdose to de=
rive benefits, often in hope of alleviating anxiety or sharpening focus. Ot=
hers in tech said they take full doses of a drug=E2=80=94using the term mac=
rodose=E2=80=94as they try to reach a high that will lead to a new disrupti=
ve idea. Goldfield describes this as =E2=80=9Cego death,=E2=80=9D an experi=
ence when a user gets to the core of their being and =E2=80=9Clets go.=E2=
=80=9D</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As well as with corporate strategy decisions:<=
/p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Tim Sae Koo was the founder of a digital marke=
ting startup in San Francisco when he discovered psychedelics at the Coache=
lla music festival in 2014.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He said they helped him realize he had started=
 his business to make his mother proud, and that it was time to sell. =E2=
=80=9CA lot of that kind of exploration in my psychedelic experience helped=
 give me a clarity that I had started the company from a place of a wound,=
=E2=80=9D he said.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/31919120.257399/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlua=
W9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDktMTMvY3J5cHRvLXdhbnRzLXNvbWUtc2VjLXJ1bGVzP2NtcGlk=
PUJCRDA2MjcyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV=
0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDYyNyZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b852=
4a319a23cBd216b1be" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> previously suggested</a> that some large per=
centage of M&amp;A activity might be driven by executives who want to avoid=
 spending time with their children. I have less of an intuition for how muc=
h M&amp;A activity is driven by executives achieving a breakthrough, via th=
erapy or psychedelics, in understanding their relationship with their paren=
ts, but it=E2=80=99s surely some. (This is the plot of <em>Succession</em>?=
) M&amp;A bankers should be leading ayahuasca retreats; when the drugs kick=
 in they can be like =E2=80=9Cyour mom is proud of you now, time to sell, h=
ere=E2=80=99s a pitchbook with some indicative valuations.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There are, however, corporate governance and d=
isclosure questions:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Silicon Valley has long had a tole=
rance toward drug use=E2=80=94many companies don=E2=80=99t test employees r=
egularly=E2=80=94but the phenomenon is worrying some companies and their bo=
ards, who fear they could be held liable for illegal activity, according to=
 consultants and others close to the companies.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Your general model might be that early-stage s=
tartup investing is about identifying visionary ideas people, and mature-pu=
blic-company governance is about making sure that companies are run by resp=
onsible adults, and it is not always the case that the visionary ideas peop=
le are (or grow up to be) the responsible adults. There is a transition, be=
tween early-stage and mature companies, that might require a change of pers=
onnel or at least a change of behavior. The hallucinogens might be required=
 for the ideas people and forbidden for the responsible adults. If you are =
a certain sort of tech founder you might start taking hallucinogens because=
 your board of directors loves them, and then later have to stop taking hal=
lucinogens because your board of directors hates them.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also of course everything is securities fraud:=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31919120.257399/a=
HR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9peD9kb2M9L0FyY2hpdmVzL2VkZ2FyL2RhdGEvMTMxODYwNS8w=
MDAwOTUwMTcwMjMwMDE0MDkvdHNsYS0yMDIyMTIzMS5odG0jcmlza19mYWN0b3Jz/607f07ceef=
4b8524a319a23cB3a93862b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" tar=
get=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; b=
order-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style:=
 solid; background-color: #ccc;">Tesla Inc.=E2=80=99s 10-K</a> says things =
like =E2=80=9CWe are highly dependent on the services of Elon Musk, Technok=
ing of Tesla and our Chief Executive Officer=E2=80=9D and discloses that =
=E2=80=9Che does not devote his full time and attention to Tesla,=E2=80=9D =
but it does not mention ketamine. Probably someone is going to sue about th=
at eventually.</p>
