le medical infrastructure. The banking system enables a higher rate of crea=
tion of these goods than would prevail in an environment where only risk ca=
pital was available to fund them. This is its main social purpose; the chec=
king accounts and payments infrastructure and tastefully decorated branches=
 and bonus checks are all consequences of it.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We have been talking about this a lot because =
it has broken down a bit: People have=C2=A0<em>noticed=C2=A0</em>that banks=
