<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One banking service is that if you have $1,000=
 in your bank account and you go into your bank and ask to withdraw $100 th=
ey will hand you five $20 bills. This is not the service that, like, Jamie =
Dimon touts in his investor letter at the front of the annual report; it is=
 neither glamorous nor lucrative.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footn=
ote-1" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bo=
ttom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !i=
